---
title: Township Skip
hidden: false
---
The Township Skip lets players bypass [Oolacile Township](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/oolacile-township) entirely to reach [Manus](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/manus-father-of-the-abyss) more quickly. To perform this skip the player uses different sort of [fall damages cancels](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel).

## How to perform this skip ?

- The easiest way to perform this skip is by using [**meme rolls**](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel#air-rolls) combined with **Fall Control** and a lot of stamina, as shown in [**this video**](https://youtu.be/pJDrzVDH-7s).
- The second easiest way to perform this skip is by using [**meme rolls**](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel#air-rolls), a lot of stamina, and the [**FAP ring**](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/ring-of-favor-and-protection) in order to perform more rolls than would normally be possible without it, as shown in [**this video**](https://youtu.be/s5lVY_6BzEY).
- The hardest way to perform this skip is by using [memerolls](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel#air-rolls) combined with [delayed rolls](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel#delayed-rolls). This version is way more precise but doesn't require anything else than a memeroll setup, as shown in [**this video**](https://youtu.be/jx9jhhk2ng0).
